Speaking to the Daily Mirror's Goal Time: 'I think in fact that City have to rebuild the team, not only in a couple of positions, but across the whole team.

'I think Mangala has been a terrible signing. He's shown nothing so far. Fernandinho and Fernando, for me, are not top quality Premier League players.

'Aguero is having a very ordinary time, [Stevan] Jovetic will soon be off, [Samir] Nasri and [Jesus] Navas too, all for me, by their standards, have had very poor seasons.'

